[normal]What mechanisms are there for Government to increase investment in strategic roads and attract new investors? Are there good examples from other countries that could be applied in the [bold]UK[bold]? [bold]Network wide road tolling 
[normal]might in future 
[normal]offer important 
[normal]opportunities t
